     6→// This module offers a high-level, type-safe Redis response-caching facility
     7→// that can be consumed by the Command/Query service layer.  It is intentionally
     8→// generic so that REST controllers, GraphQL resolvers or any background job can
     9→// opt-in to transparent caching with minimal boilerplate.
